Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:24.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好 欢迎来到Grand Tour特别节目\N{\fs90}Hello and welcome to a Grand Tour special,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们将从这辆车开始 大众甲壳虫\N{\fs90}which begins with this: the Volkswagen Beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:29.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都不喜欢这辆车\N{\fs90}It's a car we hate very much
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:32.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,只有纳粹和嬉皮才喜欢这车\N{\fs90}because it appeals only to Nazis and hippies,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:36.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,而我们 明显两个都不占\N{\fs90}and we are neither of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:38.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 如果你卸下车身\N{\fs90}However, if you remove the bodywork
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:41.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,套上个更有趣一点的\N{\fs90}and replace it with something a bit more fun -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,像这样的东西\N{\fs90}something like this--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,你就造了辆沙滩车\N{\fs90}you end up with a beach buggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,简直妙不可言\N{\fs90}and that's brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:48.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都爱沙滩车\N{\fs90}We love beach buggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:50.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而 威尔曼先生却颇有微词\N{\fs90}However, Mr. Wilman disagrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:53.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,他说 这东西真有那么好的话\N{\fs90}He says that if they'd been any good,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:54.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们肯定会流行起来了\N{\fs90}they would have caught on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:57.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而并没有流行过\N{\fs90}and he points out that they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以他想了个计划\N{\fs90}So he hatched a plan. And it's this:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:04.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,他让我们仨一人买一辆甲壳虫\N{\fs90}he said all three of us must buy a Volkswagen Beetle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:06.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,把它改成沙滩车\N{\fs90}turn it into a beach buggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:07.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后去一个\N{\fs90}and then report with it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:12.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,荒芜 崎岖 偏远的地方碰头\N{\fs90}to a wild, rugged and extremely remote place--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:16.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这里 纳米比亚的沙滩\N{\fs90}here on the coast of Namibia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是我的杰作\N{\fs90}This is what I've built.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车和\N{\fs90}It's as close as you can possibly get
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:48.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,1964年 布鲁斯 梅耶斯造的\N{\fs90}to the original 1964 beach buggy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,初代沙滩车非常像\N{\fs90}built by Bruce Meyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:56.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,各种零件都来自50年代甲壳虫\N{\fs90}Underneath, it is a 1950s Beetle--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:58.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,底盘 悬架\N{\fs90}Beetle floorpan, Beetle suspension,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,引擎 变速箱\N{\fs90}Beetle engine, Beetle gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有前灯\N{\fs90}It's got Beetle lights on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,我甚至还装了甲壳虫时速表\N{\fs90}I've even got a Beetle speedometer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,和甲壳虫轮毂罩\N{\fs90}and Beetle hubcaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,堪称完美\N{\fs90}It's brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:15.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,这和史蒂夫麦昆在\N{\fs90}This is a beach buggy very like the one that Steve McQueen drove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,偷天换日里开的那辆几乎一模一样\N{\fs90}in the original Thomas Crown Affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且它在电影里就够好的话\N{\fs90}- And if it's good enough-- - (HORN TOOTS)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:23.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢天啊 -哈哈\N{\fs90}- Oh, God. - Ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,我被强行拖入了70年代\N{\fs90}I've been joined by the 1970s.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:31.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fs90}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:35.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯造的是沙滩车的历史\N{\fs90}James May has built what a beach buggy was,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:39.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,而我这 则是它可能的未来\N{\fs90}what I've built is what a beach buggy can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你有那么点想象力\N{\fs90}...if you have a bit of imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,和紫色金属亮片漆的话\N{\fs90}and some purple metal-flake paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈\N{\fs90}Ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:58.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里 我觉得就是冒险的起点了吧\N{\fs90}There, I believe, is the start point of our adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,真是个好地方啊\N{\fs90}What an extraordinary place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:11.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,很惊人 你看 那么多海豹\N{\fs90}It's amazing, isn't it? I mean, more seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,大卫 艾登堡唯一没告诉我们的就是\N{\fs90}What David Attenborough never told us about those
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,海豹闻起来有多糟糕\N{\fs90}is how bad they smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:21.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,可惜 在我们的自然课堂继续下去之前\N{\fs90}Sadly, before our nature documentary could go any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:24.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,理查德 哈蒙德在雾中出现\N{\fs90}Richard Hammond emerged from the mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:28.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢你看 那不是沙滩车吧\N{\fs90}Ooh, hello. That's not a beach buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,-对吧 -我不会这么叫它\N{\fs90}- Is it? - Well, I wouldn't call that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,-啊哈 -噢天啊\N{\fs90}- Ah-ha! - Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 丁丁\N{\fs90}Ladies and gentlemen, Dick-tari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,请看\N{\fs90}Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,你穿的啥\N{\fs90}What are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,你穿的那是什么\N{\fs90}What are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可是在非洲啊\N{\fs90}Well, I'm in Africa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:44.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,你这裤子\N{\fs90}- (JAMES LAUGHS) - These trousers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,买的时候店员是不是说\N{\fs90}did they say in the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,这裤子是黄色的 您真要买吗\N{\fs90}"I'm afraid they are yellow, sir"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,当你一走 他们就说 太好了\N{\fs90}When you left, they went, "Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,那东西挂了20年终于卖掉了\N{\fs90}20 years we've had those on the hanger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fs90}- - Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后我们就得开着这车\N{\fs90}And then we must move over to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,-嗯哼 -我们被要求\N{\fs90}- Yeah. - We were told
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,造一辆沙滩车\N{\fs90}to build beach buggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,-嗯哼 -沙滩车\N{\fs90}- Yes. - Beach buggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这不是沙滩车啊 -不是\N{\fs90}It's not a beach buggy. It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是啊\N{\fs90}It is a beach buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是 它还有车顶呢！\N{\fs90}It isn't a beach buggy. It's got a roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且这里面根本就没甲壳虫元素啊\N{\fs90}There's no Beetle in here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 里面有甲壳虫的引擎\N{\fs90}Yes, there is. Beetle engine in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 这个立体车架...\N{\fs90}OK, this space-frame chassis...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是啊 -也是从甲壳虫上来的？\N{\fs90}- Yeah. - Is it from a Beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:16.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是 -这些巨大的悬架\N{\fs90}- No. - These enormous suspension components -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,甚至都不能好好的呆在车身里\N{\fs90}that don't even fit under the bodywork.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:21.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你在后面竟然放了两个悬挂 -双减震嘛\N{\fs90}- You've got two lots of suspension at the back. - Twin shocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:25.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,-双减震？ -我喜欢这种越野的气氛\N{\fs90}- Twin shocks? - I like an off-road sort of vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:28.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,要想到终点 我们得开过一片海滩\N{\fs90}To get here, we had to drive on a beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,-嗯哼 -我们的车没问题\N{\fs90}-Yeah. -Ours have made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:33.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车可不需要两个避震器\N{\fs90}I didn't need two lots of rear suspension on mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:33.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs90}Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,你看吧 当时只告诉我们来非洲\N{\fs90}Look, we were told to come to Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:39.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果能具体点 来圣莫妮卡海滩 那...\N{\fs90}If we'd been told to go to Santa Monica Beach, then this, with its...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:42.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,...蠢得不可思议的骚气涂装...\N{\fs90}...incredibly vivid paint...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:45.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是我见过最有金属感的车身了\N{\fs90}That's the most metal flake I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,世界上有没有那么一个沙滩\N{\fs90}Any beach in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,-等下 那是什么？ -那是引擎\N{\fs90}- Hang on, what's that? - That's the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,- V8! -那是什么引擎？ -V8！\N{\fs90}- What engine is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,我把V8放进了沙滩车！\N{\fs90}I've put a V8 in a beach buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 其实 你没放进去\N{\fs90}Well, no, you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,你这车也太紧凑了\N{\fs90}You've parked your beach buggy quite close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,它都不在车里！\N{\fs90}It's not in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,-它不在里面 -不在\N{\fs90}- It isn't in it. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,你强塞进了一个V8\N{\fs90}You've reversed into a V8,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,但用力还不够猛\N{\fs90}but not quite hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,它只进去了三分之一\N{\fs90}It's only gone in a third of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们知道要把V8引擎\N{\fs90}Do you have any idea how difficult it is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,塞进沙滩车里有多难吗\N{\fs90}to fit a V8 to a beach buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,-根本就不合适啊 -明显不可能\N{\fs90}- Well, it doesn't fit! - It's obviously impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 是不可能\N{\fs90}Exactly, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这不是普通的v8\N{\fs90}This is no ordinary V8.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,它本来是\N{\fs90}It started out in life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:17.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,路虎的3.5升V8引擎\N{\fs90}as a 3.5 litre V8 from a Range Rover,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:22.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,不过我微调了 现在它能输出180马力\N{\fs90}but I've modified it, so it produces 180 horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能说一句吗 你们在怀疑\N{\fs90}Can I just say, you were doubting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的沙滩车的可靠性\N{\fs90}the credibility of mine as a beach buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs90}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙滩车的定义\N{\fs90}The defining characteristic of a beach buggy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:32.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,是一个风冷 四缸甲壳虫引擎\N{\fs90}is an air-cooled, flat-four Beetle engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 那不是引擎 詹姆士\N{\fs90}No, that's not an engine, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,那只是个风扇\N{\fs90}That's just a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,你有多少马力？\N{\fs90}How many horsepower does yours have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,94!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我这辆车的马力是你的两倍\N{\fs90}So I have twice as many horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你要知道 -发动机并不在车里啊\N{\fs90}- Shall I tell you something? - They're not in the car, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,-他们在啊 他们离得很近 -是啊\N{\fs90}- They are, they're near it. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,很有趣 不是吗  我是说 整个就是--\N{\fs90}It's interesting, isn't it? I mean, that is an entire--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,没啥意思\N{\fs90}Nothing about that is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是一张空白画布\N{\fs90}This is a blank canvas
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以尽情挥洒个性\N{\fs90}onto which you could paint your personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没错 -但你的不是\N{\fs90}- Yes. - Yours has got
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,V8就那么挂在屁股上\N{\fs90}a prolapsed V8 hanging out of its backside
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有那糟糕的涂装\N{\fs90}and terrible paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的就很华丽\N{\fs90}Mine is a rather magnificent
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,Daktari主题的越野风格\N{\fs90}"Daktari"-themed off-roader. ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,那上面什么都没有啊！\N{\fs90}That's got nothing on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你能解释... -这有点太无聊了\N{\fs90}- You can express... - It is a bit boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,...你的全部个性和标准\N{\fs90}...all your personality, and it's standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是...你什么意思 标准？\N{\fs90}It's not... What do you mean, standard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是辆沙滩车\N{\fs90}It's a beach buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,这很高雅啊\N{\fs90}- It's tasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs90}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:13.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢 -蝙蝠电话\N{\fs90}- Oh. - The bat sat-phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们收到一条来自...\N{\fs90}We've got a message from...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,制作人先生的信息\N{\fs90}Mr. Wilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,继续说\N{\fs90}Right, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,“既然你们都开上了沙滩车...”\N{\fs90}"Since you're in beach buggies..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们俩确实是\N{\fs90}Well, us two are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,“既然你们已经开上了沙滩车，\N{\fs90}"Since you're in beach buggies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,"就应该开向沙滩”\N{\fs90}you will now drive to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,额\N{\fs90}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,额 你不觉得\N{\fs90}Uh...do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,他的常识离家出走了吗\N{\fs90}he's taken leave of his senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,他地理从来没好过吧\N{\fs90}Well, he was never that good at geography, was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,确实不好 你们现在要开到沙滩上\N{\fs90}No, he wasn't. "You'll now drive to the beach."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,等下 哦不 这后面还有\N{\fs90}Hold on. Oh, no, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们将要去到的沙滩\N{\fs90}"The beach to which you will drive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:42.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,位于鳄鱼出没的库内内河边\N{\fs90}is located on the crocodile-infested Kunene River
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:47.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,纳米比亚的最北边 与安哥拉接壤\N{\fs90}at the northernmost point of Namibia, where it meets Angola.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,远在1600公里之外\N{\fs90}It's 1,000 miles away."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:54.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,- 有1600公里  - 1600公里\N{\fs90}- 1,000 miles? - 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在最需要的是一张地图\N{\fs90}What we needed at this point was a map,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,于是我们决定沿着海岸北上\N{\fs90}so we decided to head north up the coast
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:02.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,找到一个最近的村庄\N{\fs90}and find the nearest town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:05.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\fs90}Let the journey begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,开着这样的车会是怎样的旅行呢\N{\fs90}And what a journey it would be in these cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:16.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些车诞生在一个有趣的时刻\N{\fs90}cars that were born in interesting times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是1964年\N{\fs90}So, it's 1964,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,"青少年"这个词正开始出现在\N{\fs90}the word "teenager" has started to appear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,世界各国的字典里\N{\fs90}in the world's dictionaries,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:28.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,人们开始欣赏新式音乐\N{\fs90}people are listening to new types of music,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们在接触着新鲜事物\N{\fs90}they're smoking new types of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:35.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,接着 在加州 沙滩车出现了\N{\fs90}And then, in California, the beach buggy arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太完美了\N{\fs90}It was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,男孩女孩 沙滩烧烤\N{\fs90}Girls and boys, beach barbecues...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,首要的设计准则是前轮轮眉要平坦\N{\fs90}The first design criteria was that the front fenders were flat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你可以在上面喝啤酒\N{\fs90}so you could stand a beer on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,汽车就该这么设计!\N{\fs90}That's how you design a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:08:00.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,吉米亨德里克斯有一台沙滩车 尼克松总统没有\N{\fs90}Jimi Hendrix had a beach buggy and President Nixon didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就说明了很多问题吧\N{\fs90}Tells you all you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,我真正喜欢沙滩的地方是\N{\fs90}What I really like about the beach buggy is that it's a testament
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:12.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是对人类精神胜利能力的证明\N{\fs90}to the ability of the human spirit to triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为有人会看着甲壳虫说\N{\fs90}Because somebody looked at the Beetle and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:18.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 这是世界上最万恶独裁者的遗存\N{\fs90}"Well, that's the legacy of the world's worst dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们把它改成一部沙滩车吧\N{\fs90}Let's turn it into a beach car."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,在烟雾迷离中\N{\fs90}After a lonely hour
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,孤单的北行一个小时之后\N{\fs90}of driving north through the swirling mist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们依然没有找到一个村子\N{\fs90}we still hadn't found a town,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:35.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我们找到了些别的\N{\fs90}but we did find something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs90}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你们\N{\fs90}I'll tell you what,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:01.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,它上沙滩的时候\N{\fs90}he must have been going at a right old lick
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:01.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,直接就这么蹭过来了\N{\fs90}when he hit the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,肯定的\N{\fs90}He must have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯 海在那边\N{\fs90}Right, the sea is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,有将近两公里呢\N{\fs90}That's half a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:07.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,我也觉得\N{\fs90}I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,他先冲上沙滩\N{\fs90}So he got it up the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后类似做了一个手刹过弯\N{\fs90}and then sort of did a handbrake turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:13.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,开足动力 把它滑上来  你去哪儿拉手刹\N{\fs90}-Power-slided it in. -How do you do a handbrake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,讲真啊 它到底怎么到这里的\N{\fs90}How did it get here, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:18.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想说 我的乳头激凸了\N{\fs90}Can I just say... my nipples are erect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 外套磨的  不是\N{\fs90}- What, 'cause of this jacket? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,太冷了\N{\fs90}- Oh. - It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,确实太冷了啊 嗯 是挺冷的\N{\fs90}- It is, isn't it? - It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可不是一个明智的穿衣策略\N{\fs90}That's an unwise wardrobe strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊 但是你知道\N{\fs90}Yeah, well, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,非洲 在沙滩上 我以为\N{\fs90}Africa, on a beach, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:33.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,我也这么想的  我被震惊了\N{\fs90}- So did I. - I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙滩上有海上的哈雾\N{\fs90}The beach has got the sea haar on it -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有薄雾 浓雾 寒冷\N{\fs90}mist, fog, cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你看那边 嗯哼\N{\fs90}- If you look over there... - Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,阳光 蓝天\N{\fs90}...sunshine, blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:46.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不往内陆走  找沿海公路\N{\fs90}- Why don't we just go inland... - The coast road.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,找一个能把我们带到城镇的沿海公路\N{\fs90}Find the coast road which will take us to a town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,那边艳阳高照 是个更好的注意\N{\fs90}And that'll be in the sun. That's a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,在提出了计划之后\N{\fs90}With a plan worked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,是时候再次上路了\N{\fs90}it was time to get moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊\N{\fs90}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,你把电瓶也改装了么\N{\fs90}Did you modify the battery as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs90}- (IGNITION FAILS) - Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,很明显电瓶没充上电 不会吧\N{\fs90}- It's obviously not charging up. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我没改电瓶\N{\fs90}Because I didn't modify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:11.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs90}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:15.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我看看我的还好不好使\N{\fs90}I'll just see if mine works.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,好耶  我也试试我的吧\N{\fs90}- Oh, yeah. - Let me just try mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:20.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fs90}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,推推看  啥\N{\fs90}- Push? - Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:25.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,你能帮我推一下么\N{\fs90}- Can I have a push?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:35.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,在节目组帮我重新上路后\N{\fs90}After the film crew had got me going,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,我用我强大的马力去追其他人\N{\fs90}I used my massive horsepower to catch the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:49.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是当我们又碰面的时候\N{\fs90}But by the time we were back together again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,天已经黑了\N{\fs90}it was going dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:55.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,正如你回头看到的 太阳已经落山了\N{\fs90}The sun, as you can see over my shoulder, has set,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们还是没找到一条路\N{\fs90}and we still haven't found a road.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:01.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且还开始变得非常非常的冷\N{\fs90}It's also going to be very, very, very cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,开灯\N{\fs90}Lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们一定要找到一条路啊\N{\fs90}We have got to find this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:18.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,在这种地方开夜车\N{\fs90}This is not going to be too clever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,可不明智\N{\fs90}in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我随意地把手电筒安装在\N{\fs90}I've rather crudely rigged up my torch,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,挡风玻璃的框架上\N{\fs90}wedged in the windscreen rail,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:35.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,希望你们能通过镜头看到我的遗言\N{\fs90}in the hope that you can see my last pieces to camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:40.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 见鬼\N{\fs90}Oh, bollocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于\N{\fs90} Finally, though
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们好像要转运了\N{\fs90}it looked like our luck had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 你好 你好\N{\fs90} Ooh, hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs90} What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这不是宾馆 -不是\N{\fs90}- It's not a hotel.- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,有粪便的味道\N{\fs90} It smells of excrement!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦哇 看这个\N{\fs90}  Oh, wow, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里依然还有 像盘子\N{\fs90} There's still, like, plates
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,杯子 茶碟和别的东西在这里\N{\fs90}and cups and saucers and things in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以告诉你这是什么\N{\fs90}I'll tell you exactly what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一个废弃矿山\N{\fs90}It's an abandoned mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:21.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们在纳米比亚采矿不是吗\N{\fs90}They do mine round in Namibia, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:22.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们采什么矿\N{\fs90}What do they mine for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,-钻石 -钻石？\N{\fs90}- Diamonds.- Diamonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:27.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 但如果采到了 他们是不会走的\N{\fs90}Yeah, but they wouldn't have left if there were any.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,很明显他们离开了 而且不止一天两天了\N{\fs90}They obviously left,and not yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:35.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,看着 这里没有路不是吗\N{\fs90}Look, there's no road here,is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没有 -没\N{\fs90}- No.- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:37.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,除此之外\N{\fs90}Apart from anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在黑夜里可找不到路\N{\fs90}we can't find our way around in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:40.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们没办法导航\N{\fs90}cause we can't navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,-其实我可以 -怎么做\N{\fs90}- Well, I can.- How?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怎么做 -星星\N{\fs90}- How?- Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不 你不能 -我可以\N{\fs90}- No, you can't.- I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:48.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,我承认我很多事都做不到\N{\fs90}I can't do very many things, I admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,任何事 但是这个我能做到\N{\fs90}...anything,but I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么用星星来导航\N{\fs90}How do you navigate by the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,恩 找到南十字\N{\fs90}Uh...find the Southern Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,可以 但是那可太复杂了\N{\fs90}Yeah, but that's really complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:58.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 你想睡在粪坑里吗\N{\fs90}Right, do you want to sleep in the excrement mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 这个排除\N{\fs90}No, this is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我们必须继续走\N{\fs90}So, we have to keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管我们喜欢与否 直到我们找到\N{\fs90}whether we like it or not,till we find...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们必须 所以听着\N{\fs90}We have to, so listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:08.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,我应该能找到南十字星\N{\fs90}I shall find the Southern Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不能用锤子来找南十字星\N{\fs90}You can't find the Southern Cross with a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,我找到了 哈哈我找到了 它在那里\N{\fs90}I've found it!Ha! I've found it. It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,它就像个风筝\N{\fs90}It's like a kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那里的那个？ -对\N{\fs90}- That one there?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是风筝状的 有点像\N{\fs90}It's a kite shape. It's sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在 你把长轴 \N{\fs90}Now, you take the long axis, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:22.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好的 -嗯\N{\fs90}- Yes.- Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,画一条假想线\N{\fs90}And draw an imaginary line
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:28.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,穿过它 直到地平线\N{\fs90}through it,down to the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了吗 现在你把它相交\N{\fs90}Yes? Now, you intersect it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:33.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,于另外两颗星之间的连线\N{\fs90}from a line drawn between two other stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,这两条假想线的交点\N{\fs90}and where those two imaginary lines meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,正下方就是正南方\N{\fs90}directly underneath it is due south.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以如果这两个\N{\fs90}So if it's those two--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,也正是这两个 我能确定\N{\fs90}which it is, I'm sure of it--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,你画根线\N{\fs90}you draw a line...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦这真是个坏主意\N{\fs90}Oh, this is a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在把命交给了一只\N{\fs90}We are now trusting our lives to an orangutan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,觉得自己是帕特里克 摩尔的大猩猩\N{\fs90}who thinks he's Patrick Moore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:04.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,在那里  这里有两颗星\N{\fs90}There it is. There's the two stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:07.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,画根线\N{\fs90}Draw a line...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:11.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,你没给我什么指示啊 杰里米 方向对吗\N{\fs90}I'm not getting many directions from you, Jeremy. Is this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,你有点朝右过头了\N{\fs90}You're heading a little bit too much to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,你得朝左一点\N{\fs90}You need to go left a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:19.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,好 好 哦我真是太自信了\N{\fs90}Good, good. Oh, I'm so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:24.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,等到太阳升起你们就会尝到屈辱的滋味的\N{\fs90}You two are going to be eating humble pie when the sun comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:30.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管杰里米·哥伦布\N{\fs90}Despite the confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,是如此自信满满\N{\fs90}of Jeremy Columbus,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:35.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有路出现\N{\fs90}no road appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦这太糟糕了\N{\fs90}Oh, this is grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs90}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:48.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经开了很长很长的时间了\N{\fs90}I've been on the go a very, very long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:53.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计们 对不住了 我不想再往前开一点点了\N{\fs90}Guys, I'm sorry. I'm not driving another inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:55.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fs90}I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在是凌晨三点\N{\fs90}It's three o'clock in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经被榨干了\N{\fs90}I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:01.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,他说的很有道理\N{\fs90}He does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,第二天早上\N{\fs90}The next morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们睡在沙子上醒来\N{\fs90}we woke, having slept on the sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,蜷缩在引擎边上为了取暖\N{\fs90}huddled round our engines for warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,你个笨蛋 那是什么\N{\fs90}You muppet. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs90}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:49.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯什么嗯\N{\fs90}"Um" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:52.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,我从不知道 纳米比亚有两个海\N{\fs90}I never knew Namibia had two seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,它才没有两个海\N{\fs90}It doesn't have two seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有 它有一个巨大的C(Cleckson)在这里\N{\fs90}No, it has one massive "cee" in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,一个巨大的 愚蠢的C\N{\fs90}One massive, stupid "cee"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,将我们带回到了我们出发的地方\N{\fs90}that's navigated us back to where we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:00.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我可以说 -这不是我 我\N{\fs90}- Can I just say...- It wasn't my... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:03.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么我们会相信你能用星星来导航\N{\fs90}Why did we even believe you could navigate by the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,你甚至都不能读指南针\N{\fs90}You can't even read a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,有两个C  这里有C\N{\fs90}There are two "cees". There's two "cees" here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,竟然会相信那个C可以为我们指明方向\N{\fs90}for believing that that "cee" could navigate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 你没错 -我也许不能\N{\fs90}- No, you're right.- I couldn't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,真的 我无法理解\N{\fs90}Really, I don't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:17.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,超级冷 脸上像被砂纸刮\N{\fs90}Freezing cold, sandpapered on the face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你穿着件大衣呢 -它很薄 你感受过没有\N{\fs90}- You've got a coat on.- It's thin. Have you felt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,我连一件薄外套都没有\N{\fs90}I haven't even got a thin coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,我只有一件T恤 不管怎样\N{\fs90}I've only got a T-shirt. Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,我才不要和你争\N{\fs90}I'm not going to be competitive with you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,谁最冷\N{\fs90}about who's the coldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,我才是最冷的 -我们都是最迷失的\N{\fs90}- I'm the coldest!- We're all the lostest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:30.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,没关系 听着 我们不要再被困下去了\N{\fs90}Never mind. Look, let's not get bogged down
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:31.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管究竟是谁的错\N{\fs90}with whose fault it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,要不是你我们才不会被困在这里\N{\fs90}There's no being bogged down with it, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,都是你的错\N{\fs90}It was yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可以重新回到沙漠里\N{\fs90}We can either go back into the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,寻找一条路\N{\fs90}to look for a road,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者我们可以继续昨天做过的事\N{\fs90}or we can just do what we were doing yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:42.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,待在沙漠里\N{\fs90}and stay on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,至少我们知道 如果我们让海在我们的左边\N{\fs90}At least we know, if we keep the sea on our left,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:46.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们就可以往北方走\N{\fs90}we're going north.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 -这很有道理\N{\fs90}- Yes. - That's a fair point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,-让我们用海来导航 -是的\N{\fs90}- Let's navigate by the sea. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,在我们的新  好吧 稍新的\N{\fs90}With our new-- well, newish--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,预备计划下\N{\fs90}plan in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们再一次出发\N{\fs90}we set off once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:03.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在我们在的地方 这些是我们昨天留下的胎痕\N{\fs90}So here we are. These are our wheel marks from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:08.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,24小时的寒冷 悲惨\N{\fs90}24 hours of cold, misery...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,却毫无所获\N{\fs90}to achieve exactly nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:12.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是说 真的什么都没有\N{\fs90}I mean, it is exactly nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:16.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 除了这个还有这天气\N{\fs90}But, apart from that and the weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:20.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有大猩猩 别的都进展顺利\N{\fs90}and Jeremy Clarkson, it's all going really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们一路向北\N{\fs90}As we continued north,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,前日的悲惨在我们周围的壮丽景色下\N{\fs90}the misery of the previous day was banished
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:29.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,都犹如过眼云烟\N{\fs90}by the sheer bigness of our surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦这真是个令人惊叹的地方\N{\fs90}Oh, this is an astonishing place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:38.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,有个好似珠穆拉玛峰般高耸的沙丘在我的右边\N{\fs90}I've got a dune the size of Mount Everest to my right,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:41.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,大西洋在我的左边\N{\fs90}the Atlantic Ocean to my left...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,这简直如史诗一般\N{\fs90}This is absolutely epic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,这才是沙滩车之旅\N{\fs90}This is proper beach buggy driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,太阳缓缓落下 大海就在那里被浪花拍打\N{\fs90}Sun's out, sea's there with the surf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就像海滩男孩一样（乐队名称）\N{\fs90}It's like being in the Beach Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管这一切都很迷人 但是\N{\fs90}Amidst all this loveliness, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:13.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是房间里还是有个大问题\N{\fs90}there was one small elephant edging its way into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计们 我实在不想说这个\N{\fs90}Chaps, I don't want to have to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:21.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,但现在是涨潮还是退潮\N{\fs90}but is the tide coming in or going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:24.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,恩 我猜是涨潮\N{\fs90}Uh...I'm guessing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,不可能会涨到那里\N{\fs90}There's no way up the sides of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:33.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是如果潮水真的进来了这么多 看上去是这样的\N{\fs90}And if the tide comes in that far, which it does,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们就没辙了\N{\fs90}we've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,在这里必须一直开\N{\fs90}Got to keep moving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可承受不起被困在这里\N{\fs90}We cannot afford to get stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:45.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,随着几次慷慨的大脚踩油门\N{\fs90}With some generous use of the throttle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们设法逃出了\N{\fs90}we managed to get clear
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,海和沙丘的钳制\N{\fs90}of the sea-and-sand-dune pincer movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:52.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是接着我们又遇到了另一个问题\N{\fs90}But then we had another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:58.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是沙滩的尽头\N{\fs90}I'd say that was the end of the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,它怎么会这样直接到头?\N{\fs90}How does that just end like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:03.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,它就是这么到头了 -这里就是尽头\N{\fs90}It does just end. That is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且纳米比亚政府不允许我们\N{\fs90}And the Namibian government doesn't allow us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,在盐碱滩上开 而这里就是\N{\fs90}to drive on the salt pans, and that's what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:10.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就意味着 根据詹姆斯的话\N{\fs90}This meant, according to James,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们只剩一条路可以走\N{\fs90}we had only one option.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就是回到我们的起点\N{\fs90}We've got to go back the way we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是假如潮水涨进来\N{\fs90}But if the tide's coming in,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:19.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,那狭窄的通道将会变得无法通过\N{\fs90}that narrow bit will have become impassable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:23.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,因此我想到 如果看到一个好的机会左转\N{\fs90}That's why I think if we see a good opportunity to turn left,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,比如像我们昨天晚上 我们就左转\N{\fs90}like we did last night, we do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,你真是建议我们回到……\N{\fs90}Are you honestly suggesting we go back in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 我们还能去哪儿呢\N{\fs90}Well, where else can we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们要么被淹死 要么就是饿死\N{\fs90}We'll either drown or starve otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 我们只要找到一个小通道\N{\fs90}Right, we've just got to find a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:42.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们在涨潮之前进入内陆\N{\fs90}where we can get inland before the tide comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,潮水快要涨到那里了\N{\fs90}That is getting closer to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:53.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果那个发生了 我们就完了\N{\fs90}and when that happens, we've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:59.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,在我们势如破竹的前进时\N{\fs90}But as we thundered along,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙丘拒绝打开通道让我们驶入\N{\fs90}the dunes refused to open up and let us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:06.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,海来了啊\N{\fs90}That's the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,海在这里了\N{\fs90}It's the sea, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:13.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦它在冲我而来\N{\fs90}Oh, it's coming at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:16.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,我还是坚持我们没有办法逃离这里 看着\N{\fs90}I still say we can't get out here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在没有办法左转\N{\fs90}No left turn at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,正是需要V8的时候\N{\fs90}This is where you need a V8!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,卧槽\N{\fs90}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦杰里米有麻烦了\N{\fs90}Oh, Jeremy's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,那看上去可不好\N{\fs90}That is not looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:38.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,来啊 来啊\N{\fs90}Come on, come on. Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不\N{\fs90}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:47.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不 别在这出问题啊\N{\fs90}Oh, no. No, no, no. Not a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:49.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦天哪\N{\fs90}- Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯  我在海里了\N{\fs90}Uh...I'm in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这算是一个紧急情况\N{\fs90}Because it was a bit of an emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:57.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的同事决定来帮我一次\N{\fs90}my colleagues decided to help for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,走起\N{\fs90}- Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs90}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,它就这么在空转吗\N{\fs90}Is that just spinning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,它在那里被搁浅了\N{\fs90}It's beached under there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我直接开车推他就可以了\N{\fs90}I don't see why I can't push him with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好吧 那就试试 -好的\N{\fs90}-All right, then. Try. -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:10.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 算上我们\N{\fs90}James, count us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:13.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,三 二 一 走\N{\fs90}Three, two, one, away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:23.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-耶  -好 出发吧\N{\fs90}Yes!  Right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:28.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的搁浅消耗了本来就紧张的时间\N{\fs90}Me getting beached cost us time we never had in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:30.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我们还深陷其中\N{\fs90}and we were still trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\fs90}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,水位越来越高了\N{\fs90}Ah, it's coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,冲啊\N{\fs90}Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,快走啊\N{\fs90}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:21:59.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可不妙\N{\fs90}Oh, that's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:04.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,操\N{\fs90}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:12.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,宝贝加把劲\N{\fs90}Come on, baby, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:18.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,幸好 沙丘终于到了尽头\N{\fs90}Mercifully, the dunes finally started to fall away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们总算逃过一劫\N{\fs90}and we were saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:26.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们可算过来了  -没错\N{\fs90}-And we're through! -We are, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:28.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于能松口气了\N{\fs90}That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:32.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,刚才差点出不来\N{\fs90}So nearly got stuck then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:39.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们已上路36个小时\N{\fs90}We'd now been on the go for 36 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:43.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,却再次回到了起点\N{\fs90}and we were pretty much back where we started from... again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,全身湿透的我们又冷又累\N{\fs90}We were also soaked, frozen, worn out,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,由于没有食物\N{\fs90}and because we had no food with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,也是饥肠辘辘\N{\fs90}we were also hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:22:54.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,但贝爷克拉克森想来荒野求生了\N{\fs90}But then Bear Clarkson came to the rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:58.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,你能去找点浮木生火吗\N{\fs90}Cold you go and get some driftwood for a fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:02.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,你来搭个简易烧烤架之类的吧\N{\fs90}And could you fashion a rudimentary barbecue grill of some sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:05.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 你从哪找的鱼竿\N{\fs90}OK. Where did you get the fishing rod from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:07.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是我沙滩车上的天线\N{\fs90}It's my whip aerial. It's a beach buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:09.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我早有准备  -这就是鱼竿\N{\fs90}- I thought of that. - They're fishing rods.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:20.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,看 这是个完美的烤鱼架\N{\fs90}This is going to make a perfect little fish grill thing, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:26.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,你生好火了吗\N{\fs90}Have you got a fire lit yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:27.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不是负责钓鱼吗\N{\fs90}I thought you were fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:29.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊 我的车在钓\N{\fs90}I am fishing. My car's fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:32.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,-看  -是吗\N{\fs90}- Look. - Well, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我把鱼竿固定好了 -就停那了啊\N{\fs90}- Yeah, look, I've got the rods attached. - It's parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:36.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那是什么  -烧烤架\N{\fs90}What's that? That's the grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:39.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,用我工具箱里的钳子固定好架子\N{\fs90}So we hold that with the pliers from my multi-tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,把鱼切成片\N{\fs90}cut the fish up, fillet it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:44.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,你行吗 当我没问 他也就能开个罐头\N{\fs90}Can you do that? There's no point asking him. He can open a tin...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:46.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,你会片鱼吗\N{\fs90}Can you fillet a fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:48.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,-只有鱼吗  -这是在海边啊\N{\fs90}- What, is it only fish? - Well, it's the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:50.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,你还想抓什么 鸡?\N{\fs90}What did you think I was going to catch, a chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:52.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs90}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:24:00.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不是吧  -等等\N{\fs90}Oh, my God! No, wait. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.77,0:24:05.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,在哈蒙德去找浮木时\N{\fs90}While Hammond went off to get more driftwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:08.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,我和詹姆斯准备剖鱼\N{\fs90}James and I set about gutting the catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:12.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,把他的车当砧板 好样的\N{\fs90}Use his car as the table. There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:15.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那就是它的内脏 你找到了  -没错\N{\fs90}- That's his gut. Look. You've got it. - Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.52,0:24:17.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,完蛋\N{\fs90}Oh, God. Shit. Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:19.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,看 真的全掉在排气管上了\N{\fs90}it's all gone literally onto his exhaust.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:21.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,真糟糕 算了 这需要你帮忙\N{\fs90}Oh, no. Never mind. Look, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:24.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,把头切下来\N{\fs90}Right, saw its head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:27.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,-可以了  -真棒\N{\fs90}- Ah, there we go. - Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.93,0:24:30.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我觉得 但又不确定  -掉他座位下去了\N{\fs90}- I think, but I'm not sure-- - It's gone under his seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:31.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,真的吗 不会吧\N{\fs90}Oh, no. Has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.53,0:24:33.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,没事 待会再打扫\N{\fs90}It's all right, I'll get it out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:39.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,这也算是美味了\N{\fs90} Oh, it's done a treat, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.43,0:24:41.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 看这\N{\fs90}Look at this, Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.55,0:24:47.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,味道挺不错\N{\fs90}Oh, that's all right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.72,0:24:57.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是鱼的味道\N{\fs90}It tastes like fish, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.73,0:25:01.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,谁想来瓶啤酒吗\N{\fs90}OK, does anybody want a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.03,0:25:03.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你带了吗  -没有\N{\fs90}- Have you got some? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.46,0:25:06.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,去死吧\N{\fs90}- Oh, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.03,0:25:08.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,真想捅死你\N{\fs90}- That deserves a stabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.70,0:25:10.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,可不是吗\N{\fs90}That is a proper stabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:11.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,太过分了\N{\fs90}That's properly out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:16.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,午餐后\N{\fs90}After lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.24,0:25:19.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们再次向沙丘深处进军\N{\fs90}we set off once more into the dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.15,0:25:24.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,这次我们向东前行\N{\fs90}Right, so let's keep heading east.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.06,0:25:27.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们必须得找到路了\N{\fs90}And we must come to a road at some...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.46,0:25:29.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,总会有条路吧\N{\fs90}There has to be a road.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.69,0:25:32.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,但 一路走来\N{\fs90}But, for mile after mile,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.59,0:25:34.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,还真没有\N{\fs90}there wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.51,0:25:47.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是纳米布沙漠\N{\fs90}It's the Namib Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.40,0:25:52.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,纳米布在当地方言中意味着 虚无的广阔\N{\fs90}"Namib" in the local dialect means "big nothing".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.15,0:26:01.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,这定是世界上最美的沙漠\N{\fs90}It must be the prettiest desert in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.32,0:26:03.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,一望无际的沙丘\N{\fs90}It's just a sea of dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.29,0:26:11.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙丘开始越来越陡\N{\fs90} Dunes which were getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.98,0:26:14.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,老天爷 这沙丘是有多大\N{\fs90}Bloody Nora, look at the size of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.84,0:26:21.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,释放这180匹马力\N{\fs90}Engaging 180 horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.34,0:26:24.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,用两驱的沙滩车爬沙丘\N{\fs90}Climbing them in our two-wheel-drive beach buggies
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.77,0:26:27.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,变得愈加困难\N{\fs90}was becoming tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.98,0:26:33.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,加把力 你可以的 没问题的\N{\fs90}Come on, you can do this. You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.25,0:26:38.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,但凭借V8引擎 我终究还是爬上了\N{\fs90}But by deploying the V8, I was sort of all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:39.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:46.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德因为轮胎抓地力够强 也成功爬上\N{\fs90}Hammond had grippy tyres, so he was all right, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.67,0:26:49.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,一定要爬上去啊\N{\fs90}Please, make it. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.67,0:26:51.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fs90}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.36,0:26:57.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fs90}There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.01,0:27:00.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而 对于上世纪60年代的车\N{\fs90}However, back in the 1960s...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.75,0:27:05.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,别给我丢人啊 小车\N{\fs90}Come on, little car.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.66,0:27:07.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,别这样\N{\fs90}- Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.49,0:27:08.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,不要啊\N{\fs90}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.17,0:27:21.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-陷地了吗  -对\N{\fs90}- Stuck? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:23.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,两个问题 第一\N{\fs90}Two problems. Number one,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.17,0:27:26.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,他装了台90匹马力引擎\N{\fs90}he's put a 90 horsepower engine in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.13,0:27:27.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,可能实际只剩40匹了\N{\fs90}which actually is probably only 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.86,0:27:28.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,-可不是吗  -第二\N{\fs90}- Yeah. - And number two,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.91,0:27:32.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,他从来不踩地板油\N{\fs90}he will not use full power ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.22,0:27:35.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,他有90匹引擎 和5匹的脚\N{\fs90}Well, he's got a 90 horsepower engine, but a 5 horsepower foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.12,0:27:40.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌 他肯定会说 车缺缸了\N{\fs90}And I bet you any money he's saying "I had a misfire."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.99,0:27:50.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,你得把油门踩到底\N{\fs90}You've got to push the accelerator all the way to--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.42,0:27:51.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道 可是\N{\fs90}I know, but... I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.84,0:27:54.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,它有时候会缺缸\N{\fs90}It occasionally has a little misfire moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.28,0:27:55.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就滑下去了\N{\fs90}and then I lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.15,0:27:56.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就知道\N{\fs90}- He said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.84,0:28:01.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,下午继续征程\N{\fs90}And so the afternoon continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.41,0:28:05.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,咕噜号和勇敢号继续前行\N{\fs90}The Grunt Machine and the Grit Machine would forge ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.61,0:28:09.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,打死我我也不干\N{\fs90}There is no way in hell I'm doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.65,0:28:16.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,太给力了\N{\fs90}You star!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.62,0:28:17.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs90}...and then there'd be
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.99,0:28:20.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有那不可避免的通讯交流\N{\fs90}the inevitable radio exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.86,0:28:22.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米 我们怎么少了个人\N{\fs90}We appear to be a man down, Jeremy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.90,0:28:25.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯梅 你在哪\N{\fs90}James May, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.40,0:28:33.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们浪费太多时间\N{\fs90}Because we spent so much time
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.22,0:28:35.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,等待缺缸船长\N{\fs90}waiting for Captain Misfire,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.11,0:28:38.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,日落时 我们还未走出沙漠\N{\fs90}we were still in the desert as dusk fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.28,0:28:42.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,逐渐减弱的光线也意味着难以识辨路障\N{\fs90}And failing light meant it was hard to spot obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.92,0:28:45.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,状况报告\N{\fs90}Right, sit rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.69,0:28:49.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,卧  槽\N{\fs90}Jesus (BLEEP) Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.09,0:28:51.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs90}-Holy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.26,0:28:57.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs90}-Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.00,0:28:59.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,完蛋\N{\fs90} Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.50,0:29:01.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fs90}Look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.66,0:29:03.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计 我得去瞧瞧\N{\fs90}Mate, I've got to have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.41,0:29:11.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是要我的命\N{\fs90}Oh, shitty death...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.11,0:29:14.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我的刹车都抱死了 太吓人了  -看 车都给埋了\N{\fs90}- I locked up. That was just... - Look, he's buried!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.28,0:29:17.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,-车头完全埋进沙子里了  -我完全踩死了\N{\fs90}- You've buried the front. - I was completely locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.82,0:29:19.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,差点就开下去\N{\fs90}'Cause I would have gone down that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.32,0:29:20.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,好险\N{\fs90}- (RICHARD LAUGHS) - Look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.42,0:29:26.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,这次的有惊无险是在提醒我们\N{\fs90}My close shave was a reminder that, after dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.77,0:29:30.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,天色变暗 沙丘中暗藏杀机\N{\fs90}these dunes would become very, very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.54,0:29:38.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,越来越难分辨地形了\N{\fs90}It's getting harder and harder to read the terrain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.70,0:29:40.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是下坡还是上坡\N{\fs90}Is that a drop? Is that a hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.60,0:29:42.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,是往上走 还是悬崖 看不清\N{\fs90}Is that going up? Is that a cliff? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.98,0:29:47.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,危险\N{\fs90}Peril... peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.45,0:29:50.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 操\N{\fs90}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.05,0:29:52.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦我觉得那里有个坑\N{\fs90}Oh, I think there's a drop off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.99,0:29:55.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是一个漆黑的深渊\N{\fs90}It's just a black abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.08,0:29:58.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,那可能又是一个大悬崖\N{\fs90}That could be a huge cliff again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.99,0:30:03.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于 我们再也受不了\N{\fs90}Eventually, we could take no more,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.86,0:30:08.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,第二个晚上 我们又在引擎边定居了\N{\fs90}and we had to settle down for a second night around our engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.97,0:30:24.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙漠第3日
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.82,0:30:35.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们会找到路的 那里肯定有\N{\fs90}We will find a road. There must...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.37,0:30:37.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,-它不会 它不会就这样没完没了的不是吗 -不会的\N{\fs90}It can't... It can't║go on forever, can it?║- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.56,0:30:41.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,它肯定 会有一个镇 一条路 或者什么\N{\fs90}It has to... There will be a town, a road... something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.94,0:30:47.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 为了寻找救援\N{\fs90}Unfortunately, to find salvation,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.17,0:30:51.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们还需要越过更多的山丘\N{\fs90}we still had to climb more dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.31,0:30:55.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,爬上去然后又从另外一边爬下来\N{\fs90}Climb them and then get down the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.02,0:30:56.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦我的天哪\N{\fs90}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.65,0:31:00.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是悬崖啊\N{\fs90}Well, that's just a cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.06,0:31:08.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,呜 啊啊\N{\fs90}Whoa! Aargh!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:14.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇 这就是个怪兽\N{\fs90}Whoa, this is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.17,0:31:17.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 我做不到啊\N{\fs90}Oh! (BLEEP) I don't think I can do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.74,0:31:20.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇哦哦哦\N{\fs90}Whoa-ho-ho-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.45,0:31:29.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇啊啊啊啊\N{\fs90}Whoa-a-a-a-a-a!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.05,0:31:33.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们开始吧\N{\fs90}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.39,0:31:36.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们三个人 不约而同地\N{\fs90}All three of us simultaneously...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.96,0:31:41.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs90}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.95,0:31:53.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,我没有怕\N{\fs90}I wasn't scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.78,0:31:59.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦我的上帝啊\N{\fs90}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.28,0:32:03.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计们 这是迄今为止最大的一个\N{\fs90}Guys, this is the biggest yet by a country mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.99,0:32:10.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,是再说那条坡道的尺寸\N{\fs90}Is that the size of the drop
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.08,0:32:11.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,还是他那块儿发生了点什么\N{\fs90}or what's happened to his penis?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.33,0:32:16.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 看看他们都在大惊小什么\N{\fs90}Right, then. Let's see what all the fuss is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.66,0:32:18.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fs90}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.07,0:32:27.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦哦哦\N{\fs90}Oh-h-h-h-h!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.31,0:32:33.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在把轮胎打直 理查德\N{\fs90}And now straighten those wheels, Richard,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.40,0:32:34.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,掰直它们\N{\fs90}straighten them,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.45,0:32:36.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你要直直的下落\N{\fs90}because you've got to go down straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.08,0:32:40.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs90}Holy shit. Oh-h-h-h-h, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.22,0:32:42.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太吓人了\N{\fs90}That is frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.79,0:32:49.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,爱死这片沙漠了\N{\fs90}Love this desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.90,0:32:52.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,我从来也没有比在这片沙漠里\N{\fs90}I'm never, ever, ever happier
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.28,0:32:54.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,更开心过\N{\fs90}than I am when I'm in a desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.47,0:32:59.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里 这里是我去过的最好的沙漠\N{\fs90}And this... this is the best desert I've ever been to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.24,0:33:03.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,你永远也不愁没有景色可观赏\N{\fs90}You can never really lose sight of the fact, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.88,0:33:05.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,它实际上是一个\N{\fs90}that what it actually is
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.11,0:33:08.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,巨大的橙色杀人机器\N{\fs90}is a big, orange killing engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.55,0:33:13.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,一个巨大的山坡要来了 没有什么办法\N{\fs90}Now, a big crest's coming up. No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.15,0:33:16.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,不知道下面是 缓和的丘陵 还是巨大的悬崖\N{\fs90}Gentle rolling hill or massive cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.82,0:33:18.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不知道 哈蒙德\N{\fs90}I don't know, Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.72,0:33:21.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 你是认真的吗\N{\fs90}Hammond, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.06,0:33:22.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 他去了\N{\fs90}Shit, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.90,0:33:25.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德去了各位 哈蒙德去了 玩大了\N{\fs90}Hammond's gone, everyone. Hammond's gone. Big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.64,0:33:31.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 卧槽\N{\fs90}Oh, (BLEEP) me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.81,0:33:42.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,你特么是怎么下去的\N{\fs90}How the (BLEEP) did you get down that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.72,0:33:45.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,眼睛一闭就下来了\N{\fs90}With my eyes shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.12,0:33:48.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,太可怕了\N{\fs90} That was terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.79,0:33:52.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs90}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:02.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,当我们继续朝东进发\N{\fs90}As we continued to head east,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.20,0:34:04.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,地势终于平坦了一点\N{\fs90}the terrain eventually levelled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.53,0:34:13.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,这意味着我们从惊恐  变成了极度不舒服\N{\fs90}which meant we swapped terror for extreme discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.75,0:34:18.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦我的老天啊\N{\fs90}Ah. Oh, God Almighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.85,0:34:22.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不认为这些车是被设计成\N{\fs90}I don't think these cars were actually designed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.24,0:34:24.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,来经受这些惩罚\N{\fs90}to take this much punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.56,0:34:27.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,我还知道我们也不是呢\N{\fs90}- And I know we weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.16,0:34:28.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,唯一的是\N{\fs90}The only thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.89,0:34:32.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯的车比这个低 那还会更糟\N{\fs90}James's car rides lower than this and will be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.67,0:34:35.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊噢\N{\fs90}Argh! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.37,0:34:43.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,很快 这无休止的连续猛击\N{\fs90}Soon, the relentless battering
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.91,0:34:46.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,开始造成故障\N{\fs90}started to cause breakdowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.81,0:34:50.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙子 沙子进到变速杆了\N{\fs90}Sand... Sand in gear shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.98,0:34:54.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的油门被卡住了 同志们\N{\fs90}My throttle is jammed wide open, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.43,0:35:07.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是这里的空滤\N{\fs90}The problem is that every time the air filter, here,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.93,0:35:10.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,会随着我的驾驶转动\N{\fs90}turns as I'm driving along-- which it does--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.17,0:35:12.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,就会把油门拉线卡住\N{\fs90}it's jamming the throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.48,0:35:17.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,出什么事了\N{\fs90}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.78,0:35:20.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs90}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.18,0:35:22.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,油门被卡住了\N{\fs90}The throttle is now jamming
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.15,0:35:23.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,一直是全开的状态\N{\fs90}fully open all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.75,0:35:25.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 麻烦了\N{\fs90}Oh, problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.67,0:35:44.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fs90}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.03,0:35:49.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,它还会移动\N{\fs90}It is still moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.51,0:35:52.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,在队伍的前方\N{\fs90}Many miles ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.61,0:35:55.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这永无止境的颠簸 我们不得不停车\N{\fs90}we'd pulled over for a break from the endless bumps,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.93,0:35:58.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,而詹姆斯变得很有趣\N{\fs90}and James was being very interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.05,0:36:05.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个帽子好的地方在于 你可以像定日镜一样调整它的角度\N{\fs90}The good thing about this hat is you can angle it, like a heliostat,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.51,0:36:06.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,到太阳照射的地方\N{\fs90}to where the sun's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.75,0:36:08.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 没错\N{\fs90}Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.09,0:36:10.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,但你的头还是像乳头\N{\fs90}But you still look a tit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.80,0:36:13.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德真幸运 能有个伙伴\N{\fs90}Luckily for Hammond, who could do with the company,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.97,0:36:16.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,我继续移动\N{\fs90}I was back on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.70,0:36:21.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,好 现在需要一种新的驾驶风格\N{\fs90}Right, a new style of driving is now required.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.04,0:36:25.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个手臂用来转向 这个手臂用来换档\N{\fs90}This arm for steering, this arm for changing gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.53,0:36:30.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后另一只手臂用来减速 像这样\N{\fs90}and then another arm for deaccelerating, like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.08,0:36:32.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.08,0:36:33.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,加速\N{\fs90}Accelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.69,0:36:37.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,减速\N{\fs90}Deaccelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.59,0:36:40.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,有时候 当你仔细聆听\N{\fs90}Sometimes, if you listen very carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.24,0:36:42.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,甚至可以听到我的天才\N{\fs90}you can hear my genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.13,0:36:46.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,回到三人组 我们继续\N{\fs90}Back as a threesome, we continued
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.46,0:36:50.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,这看似没完没了向东的旅行\N{\fs90}with our seemingly endless journey to the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.60,0:36:54.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,只需要找到一条路 这可不再有趣了\N{\fs90}Just need to find a road now. This is not funny any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.11,0:36:56.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,受够了沙漠\N{\fs90}Enough desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.60,0:36:58.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可不想在沙漠里再过一夜\N{\fs90}I don't want another night in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.81,0:37:03.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,我闻起来太糟糕了\N{\fs90}I smell pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.53,0:37:04.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我怀疑如果我们能够\N{\fs90}And I suspect that if we manage
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.88,0:37:07.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,在今晚找到一些有人烟的地方\N{\fs90}to find somewhere tonight near civilisation,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.64,0:37:09.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们很可能会办一个庆典\N{\fs90}we should probably have a ceremonial
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.60,0:37:12.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,用内裤点起篝火\N{\fs90}bonfire of the underpants.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.29,0:37:13.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,说真的 虽然\N{\fs90}In truth, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.73,0:37:16.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们会永远困在沙漠里\N{\fs90}I thought we'd be in the desert forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.83,0:37:21.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 在下午的晚些时候\N{\fs90}But then, late in the afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.03,0:37:27.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我向前眺望 没再看到一望无际的沙海\N{\fs90}I'm looking ahead, and I'm not seeing an endless sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.47,0:37:29.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,我看到绿色\N{\fs90}I'm seeing green.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.94,0:37:33.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,树！ 那是树和灌木丛\N{\fs90}Trees! Those are trees and shrubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.62,0:37:39.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,电线杆\N{\fs90}Pylons!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.75,0:37:42.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,电线杆！ 那意味着有电\N{\fs90}Pylons! That means electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.80,0:37:48.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦耶\N{\fs90}Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.96,0:37:50.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,找到文明了\N{\fs90}Civilisation!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.40,0:37:55.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,最棒的是\N{\fs90}And then, best of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.77,0:37:57.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦我的天啊\N{\fs90}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.11,0:38:08.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我真以为又要再睡在\N{\fs90}I honestly thought we had another night of sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.98,0:38:11.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙子里\N{\fs90}-- ...in the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.00,0:38:14.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 不 看这些\N{\fs90}But, no! Look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.75,0:38:16.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,这景象实在太美好了\N{\fs90}Nicest thing I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.36,0:38:22.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以朝东 我可以朝西\N{\fs90}I could go east, I could go west...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.86,0:38:25.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管你走哪条路 总会到达某些地方 这才是重点\N{\fs90}Whichever way you go, it goes somewhere. That's the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.40,0:38:27.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一条路 它通向某处\N{\fs90}It's a road, it goes somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.10,0:38:30.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道我们刚刚做了什么吧\N{\fs90}You know what we've just done, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.37,0:38:34.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们用三辆沙滩车穿越了纳米布沙漠\N{\fs90}We've just crossed the Namib Desert in three beach buggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.08,0:38:35.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们做到了 -我们成功了\N{\fs90}- We have. - We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.37,0:38:37.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们做到了\N{\fs90}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.08,0:38:40.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有什么可以阻挡我们了\N{\fs90}There is literally nothing can stop us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.15,0:38:45.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,无可否认\N{\fs90}Admittedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.82,0:38:49.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的穿越并没有完全走直线\N{\fs90}our crossing had not exactly been as the crow flies,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.12,0:38:50.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我们找到了我们的路\N{\fs90}but we had found our road,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.89,0:38:53.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,这才是最重要的\N{\fs90}and that's all that mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:55.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦耶\N{\fs90}Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.60,0:38:57.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是我见到最好的事了\N{\fs90}That's the best thing I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.13,0:39:04.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是什么鬼?\N{\fs90}- What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.73,0:39:10.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车后面好像有东西炸了\N{\fs90}Something has just exploded at the back of my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.52,0:39:12.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs90}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.95,0:39:15.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,当我的同事们回来找到我的时候\N{\fs90}By the time my colleague shad got back to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.44,0:39:18.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,我找出了问题所在\N{\fs90}I'd worked out what the problem was.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.38,0:39:20.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实问题很简单\N{\fs90}It's really straight forward, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.42,0:39:23.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-减震器最上面的螺丝伸出来了 -对\N{\fs90}- The top bolt has come out of the shock absorber.- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.84,0:39:27.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,螺丝爆出来 射穿了冷却管\N{\fs90}It shot up, boinged into the coolant pipe,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.88,0:39:30.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,约14升的水就直接炸了出去\N{\fs90}and three gallons of water have simply burst out,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.66,0:39:33.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,溅的到处都是 唯独没进到引擎里\N{\fs90}going everywhere except into the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.53,0:39:37.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-对 -所以我只需要把那个螺栓装回去\N{\fs90}- Right.- So all I've got to dois reattach the top bolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.72,0:39:42.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,修好水管 然后找到14升的水\N{\fs90}mend the pipe and find three gallons of water...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.36,0:39:46.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,水应该可以找一个过路的司机要到 然后就能上路了\N{\fs90}which I shall get from a passing motorist,and I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.31,0:39:47.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs90}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.45,0:39:48.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,我只需要你们可以帮我\N{\fs90}All I could do with a hand with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.35,0:39:49.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,把这车子抬起来\N{\fs90}is just lifting the car up
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.71,0:39:52.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我可以重新装 呃\N{\fs90}so I can reattach the, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.35,0:39:54.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,对 不过这里会有人吗?\N{\fs90}Yeah. Well,is there anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.29,0:39:56.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这里 -我觉得迟早会有人经过这里的\N{\fs90}- There's...- I suppose a motorist will pass eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.96,0:39:59.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,他可以给你水 帮你把车子抬起来\N{\fs90}The one that gives you water will also lift it up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.84,0:40:01.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们只需要帮我抬起来一点点\N{\fs90}You could just lift it up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.68,0:40:03.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者我们可以去喝点啤酒\N{\fs90}Or we could goand have a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.90,0:40:05.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,有车来啦\N{\fs90} I hear traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.40,0:40:07.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可不想打扰你们 \N{\fs90}We don't want to interfere when you're trying to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.50,0:40:09.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,人家可能会被我们吓跑\N{\fs90}'cause we might put them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.27,0:40:15.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs90}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.52,0:40:30.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里直走应该会有个地方\N{\fs90}Somewhere along here there will be a place,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.86,0:40:34.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,有个酒吧之类的\N{\fs90}and that place will have a bar in it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.03,0:40:36.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,就会有啤酒喝\N{\fs90}that will contain beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.23,0:40:41.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,你有水吗\N{\fs90}Do you have any water?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.57,0:40:43.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈? -水\N{\fs90}- Huh?- Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.00,0:40:45.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我的散热器炸了\N{\fs90}Because the radiator has blown,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.30,0:40:46.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我需要大概14升\N{\fs90}so I need just three gallons.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.97,0:40:53.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,看 你这里有水的 我只要一桶\N{\fs90}Look, you've got some water there. Just a bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.75,0:40:56.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是辆运水车\N{\fs90}It's an actual water lorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.68,0:41:00.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且还在漏水 但是他就不肯给我点\N{\fs90}leaking water,and he won't give me any.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.96,0:41:06.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于 我找到了一个本地人\N{\fs90}Eventually,I flagged down a local
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.29,0:41:08.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,愿意分给我一些水\N{\fs90}who had water to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.53,0:41:10.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs90}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.63,0:41:13.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后我开始了维修\N{\fs90}And then I got on with the repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.89,0:41:17.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一个重新安装的避震器\N{\fs90}That is one reassembled shock absorber.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.84,0:41:19.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,把这个重新装上\N{\fs90}That's reattached,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.80,0:41:22.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样冷却系统就复原了\N{\fs90}so that's the cooling system back in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.11,0:41:29.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,经过五小时无聊的旅程\N{\fs90}After an exhausting five-hour drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.82,0:41:32.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,理查德和我终于找到了一个小镇\N{\fs90}Richard and I finally reached a town,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.38,0:41:36.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实是纳米比亚的首都温得和克\N{\fs90}which turned out to be Namibia's capital city:Windhoek,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.98,0:41:40.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们终于也找到了水\N{\fs90}and we too were taking on liquids.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.48,0:41:58.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,唔\N{\fs90}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.05,0:42:07.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,至于还在路上的某人\N{\fs90}Back out on the highway, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.49,0:42:09.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,情况就不那么乐观了\N{\fs90}things weren't so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.72,0:42:14.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在正在开的 或者试图驾驶的 是阿波罗13号\N{\fs90}What I'm driving here -or attempting to drive -is Apollo 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.79,0:42:16.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,冷却系统里进了空气\N{\fs90}There's some air trapped in the system
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.36,0:42:19.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我得在前面开一个小口\N{\fs90}and I've had to makea small hole in the front
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.60,0:42:21.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样才能够到散热器\N{\fs90}to get at the radiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.20,0:42:22.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,把那个抽出来\N{\fs90}Bled that,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.60,0:42:24.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,进到引擎里的都会抽出来\N{\fs90}bled all the stuff going into the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.34,0:42:25.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是总管\N{\fs90}This is the header pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.50,0:42:27.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,所有东西都没了 然后\N{\fs90}Everything is bled, and yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.31,0:42:29.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,开一英里 就过热\N{\fs90}you do a mile, it overheats.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.81,0:42:32.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,再开一英里 又过热\N{\fs90}Another mile, overheats.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.86,0:42:48.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们4小时开了 32公里\N{\fs90}Well, we've covered...20 miles in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.32,0:43:06.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是48公里中的第六次了\N{\fs90}This is the sixth time in 30 miles that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.78,0:43:10.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,当我的同事们享受啤酒和睡床的时候\N{\fs90}Whilst my colleagues embraced beer and bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.45,0:43:14.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,我还坚持在我一生中最艰难 最寒冷\N{\fs90}I steeled myself for the longest, coldest,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.19,0:43:18.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,最无助的夜晚\N{\fs90}most frustrating night of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.70,0:43:25.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,路况变差了\N{\fs90}The roads are getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.54,0:43:28.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,说实话 我感觉我的骨头都要散架了\N{\fs90}Honestly, my bones are going to shatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.44,0:43:30.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs90}- Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.98,0:43:39.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我有个好主意 -哦不\N{\fs90}- I've had a great idea.- Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.78,0:43:43.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天 这个太高啦\N{\fs90}Oh, shit, it's really high!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.77,0:43:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
